title: Cafe in the Park
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe serving simple food with some dairy-free and gluten-free choices. Could ask to switch cheese for hummus. Selection of teas and juices too. The company has a pro-sustainability ethic. Its other location at Pound Lane, Higginson Park, Marlow had shut down (2014).
